# Example profile's toolchain additions — merged with toolchain's base.list via the
# union of /opt/toolchain/tools.d/*.list. Same columns: <mise-name> <command> [desc].
# More illustration-of-the-add-pattern than necessity — trim or extend freely.
claude      claude
ast-grep    ast-grep  structural, syntax-aware code search & rewrite
bat         bat       syntax-highlighted file viewer
delta       delta     nicer git diff pager
gron        gron      flatten JSON to greppable lines (gron|rg; gron -u reverses)
yq          yq        query/edit YAML, JSON, TOML
eza         eza       modern ls
